{"tid":1810902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛：留意武漢不明肺炎感染個案報道　已接觸中國政府","createTime":"2020-01-04T08:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T16:17:09.000Z","uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8a2d45ff81855dfeaa40e496ec7ae66b54d406","tid":1810902,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:55:42.000Z","msg":"世界衛生組織表示，留意到武漢不明肺炎感染個案的報道，已經接觸中國政府。<br />\n<br />\n世衛發言人表示，調查正在進行中，暫時未能確定引致發病的病原體。他認為，有多種潛在可能性引致肺炎感染，可能較沙士更普遍。世衛強調，正在密切注視武漢的情況。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501001-20200104.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501001-20200104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDh3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=20e82b80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501001-20200104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5058835b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501001-20200104.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"dfb477c32969d3414b0a4804a8e5e04b2b3d97b6","tid":1810902,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c835dce4832b8da5f570dc620fe51f5b83969ffa","tid":1810902,"uid":103916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:13:24.000Z","msg":"支那肺炎"},{"pid":"eba8056944e89716ebed0406fda3e9872d1a092c","tid":1810902,"uid":146285,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:32:03.000Z","msg":"支那：反對世衛粗暴干涉中國內政"},{"pid":"7d72f40adfaa013cadbf8b9a94c99bdb81b2bb04","tid":1810902,"uid":61207,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:35:02.000Z","msg":"不明肺炎屬中國內政"},{"pid":"8bfc510fddae8d0eedaf73ada10b77b5c8da2a23","tid":1810902,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:06:57.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n----------------<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港獨立  唯一出路</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新症正名：<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國肺炎</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9e4e4a2d59005ab3ea30d8994981447043a5c439","tid":1810902,"uid":293093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:17:09.000Z","msg":"強烈譴責世衛歪曲事實，散播謠言，製造恐慌及白色恐怖，我們必須指出，世衛的虛假指控毫無事實根據，並已超出人類文明底線可接受範圍，請世衛立即收回干預中國內政的黑手。"}]}